[[File:Sith_Official.jpg|thumb|right|175px|The unknown [[Carbonite/Legends|carbonite]] [[Sith/Legends|Sith]].]]

This '''unknown Sith''' was frozen in [[Carbonite/Legends|carbonite]] and placed in a [[Carbonite Sith Tomb|tomb]] along with the [[Carbonite Sith Army]]. His life support monitors showed that his vital signs were good, and that the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] was still alive. Next to the block of carbonite holding the Sith sat an urn, whose contents were unknown. Lying in a simple stand at the top of the urn was a [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]]. The identity of this Sith and the reasons why he and the Sith Army were encased in Carbonite were unknown as of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

==Behind the scenes==
While not actually seen in the cutscene that reveals the army, the game files include this entry as "Carbonite Sith Master".

